Grouped Bar Charts
Use when having multiple groupings, and comparing values within a secondary grouping. 
Available in: Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs) and Lightning Experience.
Available in: Group, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.
For example, compare deals closed each month by lead source.
TIP Use a stacked chart to compare totals.
